### Health
GET http://localhost:8000/health

### List HCPs
GET http://localhost:8000/hcps

### List interactions for an HCP
GET http://localhost:8000/interactions?hcp_id=1

### Insights for an HCP
GET http://localhost:8000/insights/summary?hcp_id=1

### Log interaction
POST http://localhost:8000/interactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "hcp_id": 1,
  "channel": "In person",
  "interaction_type": "Detailing",
  "raw_notes": "Discussed CardioFlow access and efficacy. HCP asked for payer support and a follow-up next week.",
  "products": ["CardioFlow"],
  "topics": ["efficacy", "access"],
  "follow_up_owner": "Field Rep"
}

### Agent chat
POST http://localhost:8000/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "hcp_id": 1,
  "message": "Met the doctor today. They requested approved efficacy data and a short follow-up email."
}

### Run compliance review
POST http://localhost:8000/agent/tools/compliance_review
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "hcp_id": 1,
  "payload": {}
}

